@startuml sequence-primary-flow
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #334155
  LifeLineBorderColor #64748B
  ParticipantBorderColor #334155
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "API Controller" as API
participant "Domain Service" as Service
database "Database" as DB
participant "External Service" as External

User -> UI: Submit request
UI -> API: POST /api/resource
API -> Service: validate and execute command
Service -> DB: read/write domain data
DB --> Service: result
Service -> External: optional side effect
External --> Service: accepted
Service --> API: response DTO
API --> UI: 200 OK
UI --> User: Show result
@enduml
